  <ul>
    <li><strong>Cigna Global:</strong> Strong evacuation benefits, US network access</li>
    <li><strong>BUPA Global:</strong> Highest entry age (79), comprehensive evacuation</li>
    <li><strong>GeoBlue:</strong> US-based, excellent for Americans; strong US network</li>
    <li><strong>IMG Global:</strong> Good value, adequate evacuation coverage</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg p-6 my-8">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Get Personalized Senior Quotes</h3>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">Compare coverage and pricing from providers with strong evacuation benefits for Belize.</p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <a href="/go/cigna-global" class="inline-block px-5 py-2.5 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors font-medium" style="color: white !important;">Get Cigna Quote</a>
